body:
## Steps to reproduce the issue

jsonstr.v:
```
module submod;
	parameter DALMATIONS = "NONE";
endmodule

module top;
	submod #(.DALMATIONS("101")) submod_i();
endmodule
```

Run `yosys -p "write_json jsonstr.json" jsonstr.v && yosys -p "write_verilog jsonstr_out.v" jsonstr.json`

## Expected behavior

```
module top();
  (* module_not_derived = 32'd1 *)
  (* src = "jsonstr.v:6" *)
  submod #(
    .DALMATIONS("101")
  ) submod_i (
  );
endmodule
```

## Actual behavior

```
module top();
  (* module_not_derived = 32'd1 *)
  (* src = "jsonstr.v:6" *)
  submod #(
    .DALMATIONS(3'h5)
  ) submod_i (
  );
endmodule
```

